Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对幸运圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真教人不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对寨巴哈压倒性的兵力…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们还是得守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同盟军主力部队抵达之前,无论如何都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们切赛立欧军,并不在乎牺牲性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但凭剩下的兵力,根本就无力回天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,只要法尼利亚王驾驶\N伊斯帕农的人型装甲助阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能够使士气大振
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您务必相助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一同奋战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我梵·法尼尔担任前锋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感激您了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我要拜托你们一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们将她送至阿斯多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官立刻备妥船只
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我能帮上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在我就会想要依赖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再将你的力量,用在战争上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明拥有如此雄厚的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何还不允许我等进击呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭我等四魔军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打败那群同盟军的乌合之众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多伦卡喀大人究竟在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经由命运引导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女将落入我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对幸运圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久便能敔动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨让人哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它会冲刷一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的思念将你带回盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你也回应了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大概是头一遭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝我的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵一定会归来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都来得重要的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争根本无法满足什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无法孕育出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在不断消耗物资与人命罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个专门评断物品价值的商人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然无法阻止这种只会摧毁一切的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一点都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美到让女神都会嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不是个配得上你的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然说这些?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争很快就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无论哪一方获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的都是民众
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟那些民众一起重新再站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我还有这点用处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去当个商人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与民同在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是要成为配得上你的男人的最佳捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不晓得我有没有办法等下去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会让你的心向着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我爱你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要帮助梵?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,请你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能让光柱出现飞到寨巴哈去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去见多伦卡喀亲自拜托他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他停止这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是个说得通的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说,让你身陷危险的话,梵会难过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多伦卡喀那里就由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与命运改变装置共鸣的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会将光柱引导过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以会从比湾取回这个机械
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为这个缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是去见多伦卡喀的话,弗肯会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他特有的体贴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为他一定能让我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,我总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着要找人来让我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然等到德莱甸离去我才发现这点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你早就注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在听到你的温柔安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又会开始依赖你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想成为你的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空骑士亚连·歇萨尔,即将出征迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也将与蜜拉娜公主暂时告别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿海龙神桀齐亚庇佑你身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿你武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上级命令我们与第三十二小队一起进攻加尔佛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没参加这种大战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用决战武器?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去根本就无法攻进敌军阵营
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得一口气开条路出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是战场上还有众多我方士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要他们好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就好好体验我巴斯兰新武器的厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以待在这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得梵大人不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵达目标上空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下武器的同时上升翻转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们用了那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上空出现闪光\N什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官长,出现强光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本就不叫打仗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,是新武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑立欧舰队,咒迪亚舰队,盖丁舰队遭歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰受到冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的同盟军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然使出这种邪恶招数
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放过你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个恶魔!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算将寨巴哈赶尽杀绝是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死了也要诅咒你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵…梵他很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去阻止这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵他现在很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你很可能会死在寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了不好的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的反作用正在侵蚀着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对黑色翅膀就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色翅膀是证据?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得以性命来弥补自己\N与多伦卡喀狼狈为奸之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死的话,梵就真的孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想见到梵难过的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定能够克服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨过我的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了另一个崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会改变这种悲哀的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的人型装甲在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就全都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的因子都集合到我身边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是命运改变装置完整启动的最佳时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如我所预料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所预料?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我操纵命运让你带幻之月少女过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟还要玩弄命运到什么地步?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个蠢问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该了解我的真正想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,你也应该了解我的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来杀我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是改变命运的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作用与反作用最强的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这样就能结束战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚也能得到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么老是发生这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是发生这种令人难过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敔动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊,你就与我一同观赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对幸运圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了保护你而战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:57.34,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:05.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:13.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:19.57,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.58,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.59,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:49.56,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:57.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:05.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:13.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:19.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:34.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:49.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


